    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly representing a showroom-quality find. The exterior paint is flawless, maintaining a deep, factory-perfect shine with no scratches, chips, or imperfections of any kind. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the upholstery and dashboard looking as if they have never been touched. Mechanically, the car is perfect, providing a driving experience that is identical to when it first rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been meticulously maintained and preserved in a climate-controlled environment.",
